    • Method Detail

      • execute

        void execute​(Bridge bridge,
             String poiId,
             int layer,
             CartesianPoint position,
             Color color)
      throws CommandException,
             InternalFederateException
        Executes the command in order to add a new PoI in the SUMO-GUI.
        Parameters:
        bridge - Connection to SUMO.
        poiId - the unique ID of the PoI
        layer - the layer index of the PoI
        position - the cartesian position of the center of the PoI
        color - the color of the PoI
        Throws:
        CommandException - if the status code of the response is ERROR. The connection to SUMO is still available.
        InternalFederateException - if some serious error occurs during writing or reading. The connection to SUMO is shut down.
